<%= render :partial => 'header', :locals => { :sub => "- Services CSV Export" } %>

<div class="box_info_standout center" style="margin: 1.5em auto; width: 700px;">
  <p>
  The export is a zip archive containing 3 CSV files with tables of all Web services, SOAP operations, and REST methods in the <%= SITE_NAME %> respectively.
  </p>
  <% if latest_csv_export.blank? %>
    <p>There is no current services' export. Please use the button below to request it.</p>
  <% else %>
      <p>
        The latest services export was generated at <b><%=time_of_export(latest_csv_export)%></b>.
      </p>
      <p>
        The exports are regenerated on a regular basis. If you require a more up to date one please use the button below to request it.
      </p>
  <% end %>
</div>

<div class="center" style="margin: 0 auto; width: 700px;">
  <% if !latest_csv_export.blank? %>
    <p class="center">
        <%= link_to ("Download CSV Export").html_safe, download_latest_csv_path, :class => "button_slim" %>
    </p>
  <% end %>
  <p>
    <b><%= mail_to "#{FEEDBACK_EMAIL_ADDRESS}", 'Request New Services CSV Export', { :subject => "#{SITE_NAME} CSV Export Request", :encode => "hex", :class => "button_slim"} %></b>
  </p>
</div>



